{#- Renders the JSON-LD blocks for the data-driven pages (index, competition,
    workshop, contact, open-day-hamburg) from shared data (see
    _data/eleventyComputed.js `jsonLd`, sourced from _data/event.json +
    _data/i18n/<lang>.json). Each block is deep-equal to the hand-authored English
    block (locales differ only in the translatable strings) — EXCEPT the date-gated
    Events: index, competition and workshop each gate their Event on a date key that
    is currently absent, so they emit only Organization (+ BreadcrumbList), while
    open-day-hamburg's gate is open (real date + venue) and emits its Event. -#}
{%- for block in jsonLd %}
  <!-- {{ block.comment }} -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {{ block.data | dump(2) | safe }}
  </script>
{% endfor -%}
